items.desc: This wiki is all about my new Undertale AU NEO!Tale, which is a book series that I decided to make. This wiki is still under both edits and modifications, so lets try to keep updated on that! Also, currently, there are only 2 editors up here, me and my sister. We try our best to stay active, and we will whenever we can! Don't be afraid to message about wanting to be an editor, because the help sure is needed, but there are some guidelines to become qualified.
